Install the following packages using pip
eg: sudo pip install package-name
flask,flask_restful,nltk,sklearn
in nltk, download stopwords list and punkt model using nltk.download()

To run:
cd to the email_models_api folder
edit the last line in api.py file:
    app.run(host='0.0.0.0') #or whatever address we are going to run

then start the app by doing:
python api.py

#eg to post a request on http://127.0.0.1:5000
curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"mail1":"not intereste","mail2":"stop spamming me"}' http://127.0.0.1:5000
